         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">24 January [18]84 ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ In reply to your letter of the 17th instant ¶ , I have the honor to inform you that the Chief Secretary accedes to your request to be allowed to spend a few weeks at Warr...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">84.01.24a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Thomas Wilson</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 251, p. 1079, unit 65, VPRS 1187/P, outward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office of Victoria</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">24 January [18]84</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In reply to your letter of the 17th instant<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to G. Berry, 17 January 1884 (in this edition as 84-01-17a).</p>
               </note>, I have the honor to inform you that the Chief Secretary accedes to your request to be allowed to spend a few weeks at Warragul<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Vic.</p>
               </note> for the benefit of your health.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your obedient servant,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[T. R. Wilson]</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">The Government Botanist<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>For reply see M to Y. Wilson, 15 February 1884.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c</p>
         </div>
